spec_data.Name: texlive-skeycommand
spec_data.Description:
The package provides tools for defining LaTeX commands and
environments using combinations of parameters and keys. All the
facilities of the ltxkeys and skeyval packages are available to
the user of skeycommand.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:21:48 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Create commands using parameters and keyval in parallel
